             were indicted for <rs id="t18341016-44-off239" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18341016-44-off239" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18341016-44-off239" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18341016-44-cd240" type="crimeDate">17th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18341016-44-off239 t18341016-44-cd240"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 1s. 6d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18341016-44-victim493" type="victimName">
                           Joshua 
                           Flight
                        <interp inst="t18341016-44-victim493" type="surname" value="Flight"></interp>
